      • getAll

        public <E extends AcceloEntity<E>> List<E> getAll(EndPoint endPoint,
                                                  AcceloFilter<E> filterMap,
                                                  AcceloFieldList fieldList,
                                                  Class<? extends AcceloList<E>> clazz)
                                           throws AcceloException
        Pulls every matching entity. Be careful! you could run out of memory and slam Accelo! You can only use this method of Accelo returns a list of entities. This method will throw an exception if you try to make a call that causes Accelo to return a single entity (e.g. don't try to get a contact by id).
        Parameters:
        method -
        url -
        filterMap -
        fieldList -
        clazz -
        Returns:
        all entities for the given endpoint subject to the filters limit.
        Throws:
        AcceloException
